    "headline": "International Flavors & Fragrances (NYSE:IFF) Exceeds Q1 CY2026 Expectations",
    "summary": "Flavor and fragrance producer IFF (NYSE:IFF) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2026, but sales fell by 3.6% year on year to $2.74 billion. On the other hand, the company’s full-year revenue guidance of $10.65 billion at the midpoint came in 0.6% below analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.83 per share was 22.6% below analysts’ consensus estimates.",
